These are Puzzles for 3x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, gardening, sudoku, skydiving, board-games
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: horror, romance, time-travel, martial-arts, epic
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, rugby, tennis, ice-hockey
 1. the person watching horror movies is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who's sport is cycling##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person watching horror movies and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
 5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 7. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the person watching epic movies is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
11. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
12. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | gardening    | sudoku  | board-games | collecting    | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | time-travel   | martial-arts | epic | horror   |
| Sport         | cycling | parkour | tennis  | ice-hockey | rugby        |

