.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, chess, hiking, traveling, board-games
The people have 5 different jobs:  journalist, entrepreneur, firefighter, accountant, electrician
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, tennis, skateboarding, sailing, baseball
 1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
 2. the electrician is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is sailing##2
 3. the electrician is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is in the middle##1
 7. the journalist is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 8. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the electrician is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
11. the accountant is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is tennis##2
12. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |        2        |     3      |         4          |     5     |
| Hobby   | traveling    | chess         | card-games | board-games        | hiking   |
| Job     | entrepreneur | firefighter | accountant  | electrician | journalist |
| Sport   | skateboarding       | baseball      | sailing   | tennis           | surfing      |

