.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, mirinda
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: tennis, skiing, rowing, biathlon, parkour
The people use 5 different means of transport: quad-bike, boat, trike, bus, ship
 1. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 2. the person driving the boat is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 5. the person drinking juice is between the person driving the boat and the person drinking mirinda##2
 6. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the ship##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is the person driving the trike##1
12. the person driving the bus is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person driving the ship##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |     5      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | tea    | almond-milk   | juice          | mirinda      |
| Sport       | rowing    | parkour | skiing       | biathlon | tennis |
| Transport   | ship     | bus     | boat | quad-bike          | trike     |

