.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, comedy, crime, martial-arts, animation
5 different pets are kept: snake, horse, rat, fish, dog
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, helicopter, jet-ski, train, trike
 1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 3. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
 4. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 5. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 9. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
10. the person driving the trike is in an odd position##4
11. the person watching romance movies is on the far left or far right##3
12. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | animation    | crime  | martial-arts | comedy |
| Pet           | fish | horse    | rat | dog  | snake    |
| Transport     | trike      | jet-ski | train    | helicopter    | motorbike    |

