.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, salsa, electronic, folk, blues
There are 5 different nationalities: dutch, chinese, australian, japanese, spanish
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, taxi, helicopter, tram, car
 1. the person driving the taxi is the fan of blues##1
 2. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
 3. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
 4. the fan of blues is the japanese##1
 5. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the bike and the fan of blues##2
 6. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
 7. the dutch is on the left of the chinese##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the australian##1
 9. the spanish is on the far right##1
10. the australian is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
11. the fan of folk is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |    5    |
| Music-Genre   | blues    | dubstep        | salsa    | electronic      | folk  |
| Nationality   | japanese | australian    | dutch | chinese | spanish |
| Transport     | taxi   | tram | bike | helicopter      | car   |

