 6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person drinking juice is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
11. the fan of d&b is the person driving the jet-ski##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5    |
| Beverage      | tea  | fanta | juice | milk   | sprite  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | electronic | metal    | soul        | punk |
| Transport     | jet-ski | boat    | helicopter     | van | snowmobile    |

