.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-9::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, juice, lemonade, soy-milk
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, ambient, r&b, hip-hop, punk
5 different pets are kept: rat, guinea-pig, hamster, turtle, chinchilla
 1. the person drinking coffee is the fan of hip-hop##1
 2. the fan of r&b is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is the person drinking juice##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of ambient is the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the owner of the rat is the person drinking 7up##1
 9. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3   |    4    |       5       |
| Beverage      | juice  | coffee | 7up  | soy-milk | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | punk | hip-hop       | ambient | house | r&b          |
| Pet           | hamster   | guinea-pig        | rat   | turtle   | chinchilla        |

