 4. the person watching musical movies is the accountant##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the lizard is between the person watching scientific movies and the owner of the ferret##2
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
10. the videographer is the person watching thriller movies##1
11. the accountant is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |       5        |
| Job           | police-officer | dressmaker  | designer | accountant | videographer |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | fantasy | mystery     | musical    | thriller        |
