There 5 different types of food: radish, pear, cabbage, apple, cauliflower
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: folk, trance, blues, hip-hop, classical
 1. the person eating radish is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person drinking tea is the person eating cabbage##1
 3. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 5. the fan of trance is in an even position##4
 6. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
 7. the fan of folk is the person drinking fanta##1
 8. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking tea and the fan of blues##2
 9. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
10. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |
| Beverage      | fanta    | almond-milk | hot-chocolate   | coffee  | tea |
| Food          | apple    | radish  | cauliflower | pear | cabbage  |
| Music-Genre   | folk | trance    | blues      | hip-hop   | classical |

