 6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 8. the person eating peach is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
